<div id="review_3512973304" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3512973304" />
    <a title="Jasmine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/35278548-jasmine"><img alt="Jasmine" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3512973304?book_show_action=true">Sep 21, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jasmine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jasmine" href="/user/show/35278548-jasmine">Jasmine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3512973304" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1658233386492987738">A story about life and death, and about how we handle it. After losing his wife in a tsunami, Owen is lost and heartbroken. That is until he meets Suchin, who is lost and fighting a battle of her own. As these two characters befriend each other, they help each other through their battles. It’s such a beautiful story that mixes in some spiritual beliefs on top of the romance. There are many things about love and death that we won’t be able to understand nor control so we need to accept that. Acce</span>
  <span id="freeText1658233386492987738" style="display:none">A story about life and death, and about how we handle it. After losing his wife in a tsunami, Owen is lost and heartbroken. That is until he meets Suchin, who is lost and fighting a battle of her own. As these two characters befriend each other, they help each other through their battles. It’s such a beautiful story that mixes in some spiritual beliefs on top of the romance. There are many things about love and death that we won’t be able to understand nor control so we need to accept that. Accept it and live in the moment while appreciating what was given to you and what you have right now. These two characters did a really good job of this. </span>
