<span id="freeTextContainer7872222137219502992">I won this book in a Goodreads giveaway. The Midnight Sun was a beautiful and moving story about life and death. After Owen Sterling’s wife is killed in a tsunami while on their honeymoon in Thailand, he returns later to try to make sense of his life. While there, he meets a young, troubled Thai woman named Suchin. Together they travel to Nepal to climb the Himalayas hoping to find peace. Definitely enjoyed this reading this book.</span>

          </span>
